<plot>Seven-year-old Lily is finding it hard to understand that her parent's separation is not a temporary one. Torn between being daddy's-little-girl and mommy's-big-girl, Lily attempts to process and adapt to a new reality. At an age when most girls think about dolls, Lily dreams of a home. But in order to find a home Lily must grow up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?060884</url></doc>
